事》《戰長沙》等。","name":"馮暉","primary":false}}]}},"person_1202564_translations":{"at":1772469925576,"data":{"id":1202564,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Louis Cheung Kai-Chung (Chinese: 張繼聰, born 11 January 1980) is a Hong Kong Cantopop recording-artist, songwriter, and actor. He is an alumnus of The Hong Kong Academy for Performing Arts, majoring in acting. His first play was in 1997, and he has performed in a total of more than 20 stage plays, including the classic \"A Streetcar Named Desire\", as the main character, Stanley Kowalnski.","name":"Louis Cheung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"毕业于香港演艺学院，主修表演。1984年即以童星出道参与电影、电视和广告演出，随后涉足舞台剧表演以及为多部外语电影作粤语配音。2005年以原创歌手身份登录香港乐坛。2007年1月20日下午七时于香港富豪机场酒店与谢安琪举行结婚典礼。同年6月16日谢安琪为张诞下首名婴孩，命名为张瞻(James)。","name":"张继聪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"香港男歌手、作曲家、唱片製作人及演員。共演出過 20 多套舞台劇，包括經典名作《慾海奇女子》男主角史丹利‧柯文斯基（Stanley Kowalnski）。前香港無綫電視基本藝人合約藝員。2022 年憑電影《窄路微塵》入圍第 59 屆金馬獎最佳男主角；2023 年憑該片入圍第 41 屆香港電影金像獎最佳男主角，及榮獲第 29 屆香港電影評論學會大獎最佳男演員，此獎成為其首項影帝殊榮。","name":"張繼聰","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Trương Kế Thông","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ルイス・チョン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"張繼聰","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1290821_credits":{"at":1772469934885,"data":{"id":1290821,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":976,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Jason Statham","original_name":"Jason Statham","popularity":28.6885,"profile_path":"/pXGSq2UpcDE2NMF8LR56QZf5U1q.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"Mason","credit_id":"6644bfb8184f826